with open('testdata/models/geocoder.json', 'r') as f:
    expectedResponse = f.read()
responses.add(responses.GET,
    'https://geocode.search.hereapi.com/v1/geocode', expectedResponse,
    status=200)
response = self._api.address_with_boundingbox('200 S Mathilda Sunnyvale CA',
    [42.3952, -71.1056], [42.3312, -71.0228])
self.assertTrue(response)
self.assertIsInstance(response, herepy.GeocoderResponse)
responses.activate
